SAN DIEGANS FOR OPEN GOVERNMENT
v.
PUBLIC FACILITIES FINANCING AUTHORITY OF the CITY OF SAN DIEGO S245996 Supreme Court of California JANUARY 24, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. The request for an order directing depublication of the opinion is denied.
